  <center><h2>My India Experience</h2></center>
  <center><p>On my trip to India, I discovered beautiful temples, beaches, and friendly people. The food was amazing and every street had something new to explore.</p></center>
  <center><p>I also visited Mount everest and experienced a peaceful retreat surrounded by nature. It was a journey full of learning and adventure.</p></center>
